sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client
    participant API as GET /api/building-polygon
    participant GRB as GRB Vlaanderen WFS
    participant URB as UrbIS Brussels WFS

    Client ->> API: GET /api/building-polygon?lat=51.2211&lng=4.3997
    activate API

    API ->> API: Validate lat, lng query params

    alt Missing lat or lng
        API -->> Client: 400 { error: 'Missing lat/lng' }
    else Valid coordinates
        Note over API: Build bbox around point<br/>(±0.0005° offset, EPSG:4326)

        API ->> GRB: GET /GRB/wfs?service=WFS<br/>&version=2.0.0<br/>&request=GetFeature<br/>&typeName=GRB:GBG<br/>&outputFormat=application/json<br/>&srsName=EPSG:4326<br/>&bbox=...
        activate GRB

        Note over API,GRB: User-Agent: 'DakOppervlakte/1.0'

        GRB -->> API: { features: [...] }
        deactivate GRB

        API ->> API: Filter features by TYPE (1 or undefined)
        API ->> API: pickClosestBuilding:<br/>point-in-polygon,<br/>else nearest centroid ≤ 50m

        alt GRB feature matches
            API -->> Client: 200 { type: 'Feature',<br/>geometry: { type: 'Polygon', coordinates } }

        else No GRB match, fall back to UrbIS
            API ->> URB: GET /geoserver/UrbIS/wfs?service=WFS<br/>&version=2.0.0<br/>&request=GetFeature<br/>&typeName=UrbIS:Bu<br/>&outputFormat=application/json<br/>&srsName=EPSG:4326<br/>&bbox=...
            activate URB
            URB -->> API: { features: [...] }
            deactivate URB

            API ->> API: Filter + pickClosestBuilding

            alt UrbIS feature matches
                API -->> Client: 200 { type: 'Feature',<br/>geometry: { type: 'Polygon', coordinates } }

            else No match in either source
                API -->> Client: 200 { features: [],<br/>debug: { lat, lng, msg: 'No building found' } }
            end
        end
    end
    deactivate API
